ce George of Cambridge|Prince George]] who makes life hard for his family and the British monarchy.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2020/01/21/hbo-max-greenlights-animated-comedy-the-prince-from-creator-gary-janetti-and-20th-century-fox-television-844214/20200121warnermedia01/|title=Breaking News - HBO Max Greenlights Animated Comedy \"The Prince\" from Creator Gary Janetti and 20th Century Fox Television|website=TheFutonCritic.com}}</ref>\n\n==Production==\nOn April 17, 2020, [[Gary Janetti]] released a quarantine trailer of Prince George.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.esquireme.com/content/45534-hbo-max-releases-hilarious-new-quarantine-trailer-for-the-prince|HBO Max releases hilarious new quarantine trailer for 'The Prince'|accessdate=20 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{HBO Max}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Prince (TV series)}}\n<!--[[Category:2020s American animated comedy television series]]\n[[Category:2020s American adult animated television series]]-->\n[[Category:American adult animated comedy television series]]\n[[Category:American animated sitcoms]]\n[[Category:Upcoming comedy television series]]\n[[Category:Upcoming animated television series]]\n[[Category:English-language television programs]]\n[[Category:HBO Max original programming]]\n[[Category:Television series by Fox Television Animation]]\n[[Category:Television series by 20th Century Fox Television]]\n\n{{US-animation-tv-prog-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Use mdy dates|date=January 2020}}\n{{short description|American animated sitcom TV series}}\n{{Infobox television\n| show_name                = The Prince\n| image                    = \n| genre                    = [[Animated sitcom]]\n| creator                  = [[Gary Janetti]]\n| writer                   = \n| director                 = \n| story                    = \n| voices                   = {{Plainlist|\n* Gary Janetti\n* [[Orlando Bloom]]\n* [[Condola Rashad]]\n* [[Lucy Punch]]\n* [[Tom Hollander]]\n* [